<TEXT>
<P>
 Marcos has an interesting idea on how Edson Arantes do Nascimento acquired the 
nickname Pele. The name doesn't mean anything in Portuguese, and Pele himself 
has said he doesn't know its origins. 
</P>
<P>
 "The closest theory I have is that it came from 'light foot,' which would be 
'Pe leve,' " Marcos said. "But who knows?" HELENE ELLIOTT 
